description:

5 5x7 invitations (in each paper)

1 standard white A7 invitation envelope
1 standard white A2 RSVP envelope
1 tissue paper square

Paper options included:
• metallic pearl 
• linen texture 
• 100% post-consumer recycled
• premium smooth matte
• watercolor textured

Please visit the links above/below for more information or contact us if you cannot find an answer to your question. Thank you!

name: Alexis Wedding Invitations
description:
Vintage Lace Wedding Invitations
Shown in slate gray and ivory
Printed front and back

LISTING INCLUDES: 
25 5x7 wedding invitations 
25 A7 plain white envelopes
(RSVP card sold separately)

ORDERING: 
Add items to your cart (see below). Choose your card quantity (sets of 25). For additional items such as return address printing, you will add that 1 item, and then go to your shopping cart and type in the quantity. Go to “How to Order” (above) for more details, it contains a list you need to fill out. Mobile devices, click "More" (above).

Colors can be changed, see color chart. We offer digital off-set printing on a variety of papers including: metallic pearl, linen texture, 100% recycled, premium smooth matte and watercolor textured.

Add return addressing, tissue paper, rounded corners, upgrade envelopes and more. See "Add-ons" section in "Products" for more details, or add items using the drop-down pricing menu below (choose your "add-on", then update the quantity inside your shopping cart).

COORDINATING PIECES: 
Matching thank you cards, wedding programs, place cards, table numbers and more are available. Visit the “Wedding Day Items” in the "Products" section above.

Add reception info, directions and accommodations on the back of your wedding invitation for FREE! These wedding invitations only need 1 invite and 1 RSVP card, requiring minimal paper! We also offer 100% recycled card stock!

For quantities over 200 please contact for a quote. Note: RSVP's, reception cards and separate insert cards are all 4.5" x 5" and are not included with the price of the invitations.

name: 5x7 Snowball Christmas Photo Card - 1 Photo
description:
5x7 Christmas holiday photo card with 1 photo - snowflake snowball artwork. We will place your photos and text and send you the high resolution jpeg to print anywhere you'd like! We also offer prints, see below.

HOW TO ORDER:
• Choose from the pricing drop-down menu
• Email photo(s) and wording to ts@appleberryink.com
• You will receive a digital proof to review in about 24-48 hrs
• Once approved we will email your high resolution digital file or print your order

PRINTING:
If you want prints, select your quantity below and add to cart. Notice, there are 2 options: card stock or photo print. Your card stock paper options are: metallic pearl, linen texture, 100% recycled, premium smooth matte and watercolor textured. Note your paper preference inside when you check out.

ADD-ONS:
You may add return address printing and/or recipient address printing. Choose your option in the pricing drop down menu, then type in the quantity inside your shopping cart. Envelope printing will add a few extra days for processing. See thumbnail for how to set up your recipient address inside Excel (3 columns: 1. names 2. street 3. city/state/zip), delete other "sheets".

ENVELOPES:
Standard plain triangle flap envelopes are free with every order (except digital files). You may choose to upgrade your envelope in the drop down menu below. Choose your envelope upgrade in the pricing drop down menu, then type in the quantity inside your shopping cart (increments of 25 for card stock cards, quantities of 10 for photo card prints). 

IMPORTANT PHOTO INFO:
Photos can be sent in either .jpg or .tiff format. The resolution should be 300 dpi at the size the photo will be printed. We will alert you if the file isn't large enough. We can change photos to black and white or sepia if you'd like. 

By submitting photos you agree that you are the photographer or have permission to use the photos. You also agree to take full responsibility for using any professional photos and agree to not hold Appleberry Ink liable for using copyrighted images.

* Envelopes are not included in the purchase of a digital file.

description:

For higher quantities please contact us for a quote.

name: Guest Address Printing
description:
Have your guests addresses printed on the outside front of your envelopes. 1 Font and 1 Color from your invitation design will be used. If you have a font or color preference please write that into the information list when ordering.

This listing is for 1 address. Type in the total number of guest addresses that you will need when you go into your shopping cart.

name: Rounded Corners
description:
This listing is for 25 rounded corners. Make sure you also add in RSVP rounded corners as well. Therefore it's $14 per 25 sets of invites & rsvp cards combined.

More quantity options in the drop-down menu below.

name: Tissue Paper Inserts
description:
If you have RSVP cards we strongly encourage you to order tissue paper. It is used to protect the front of the invitation from getting any ink transferred onto it. 

It only comes in translucent white, no other colors are available.

When you stuff your envelopes you layer the RSVP card on top tucked under the RSVP envelope flap, then the tissue paper, then the invitation. Instructions on how to properly layer everything is sent along with your order.

name: Custom Map
description:
Add a map to the backside of your invitation, or purchase it as a separate insert card (add insert cards to your cart separately - pricing is inside every invitation listing).

Send a Google map link denoting all locations that you want included. Also, note any important streets that you want shown.

Once a map illustration has been started you can not get a refund if you decide not to use it. Payment is made for the time it takes to create it.

name: Custom Sample Print
description:
This listing is for 1 custom print of any design using your preferred fonts and colors. You may have your text placed, or just use the mock-up text that's currently in place.

If you wish to see a custom printed RSVP card just use the pull-down menu below and add it to your cart.

name: Custom Invitation Design
description:
Purchase this listing if you want an original design. 

This listing is not to be purchased if you want to change colors or fonts on another design, it's solely for creating an entirely new design layout. Changing colors and fonts on current designs is a free service.

Contact us first to see if the concept you have in mind is possible to do. Explain in detail what you're envisioning, send photos, color swatches or anything else that will guide us in creating a beautiful design for you.

Once you receive your first proof we will continue to make changes to the design until you approve it.
